Object ID1384

Burnt dead trees require level 1 Woodcutting to cut and give charcoal when chopped down. They look the same as some types of dead tree, except have a slightly darker tone. Burnt trees are found around the Fossil Island Volcano, in the Wilderness south of the Demonic Ruins where Callisto roams, in the Death Altar and in the Fishing Hamlet.

A similar variant of tree called burnt tree can be found on Fossil Island and also give charcoal when chopped. These trees have a different appearance but otherwise function the same.
